<br>
Both the Dagger and Seeker emblems were very visible at both battles... well done, all!<br>
<br>
Great pics, Rasha! I wondered what the carnage outside the room must look like.. I was running out and ae'ing, then mezzing, every 20 seconds or so but never stopped long enough to know what it looked like! I'm not even gonna' say how many realm points I got there.. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rollin --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/roll.gif ALT=":rollin"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
